Package: GeoLink
Title: Tools for Reading, Writing, and Listing Spatial Data on S3
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides simple, general functions for interacting with spatial data
    stored on S3-compatible object storage, supporting GeoParquet, GeoPackage,
    and GeoTIFF formats. Designed for streamlined use in collaborative and 
    cloud-based workflows.
